acerbates the\n$S_8$ tension. We also demonstrate that the addition of intermediate-redshift\ndata (from the Pantheon supernova type Ia dataset and baryon acoustic\noscillations) weakens the effectiveness of all these models to address the\n$H_0$ and $S_8$ tensions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Aug 2021 17:22:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 5 Dec 2021 17:36:23 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 20 Jan 2022 16:43:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-16"}
