that establishing permanent wage subsidies based on sectorial turnover\nrules could offer enhanced protection to middle-and high-earners and reduce\nuncertainty, the need for reform, and the risk of politically motivated\ndesigns.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Aug 2021 17:36:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-10"}
