engths. In this contribution we highlight the common\napproach adopted by the CTA Transients physics working group to perform the\nstudy of transient sources in the very-high-energy regime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Aug 2021 19:35:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-11"}
