\nsupported by nocturnal marginally stable stratification. Moderate winds lead to\n20-m tall convection across weaker stratification, weak winds to episodic <10-m\ntall shear instability across larger stratification.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Aug 2021 09:44:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Aug 2022 07:38:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-14"}
