tion in\nautonomous networks. These observations provide the basis for in-depth\ninvestigation and standardization efforts for IBN as a fundamental network\nmanagement paradigm in beyond 5G cellular networks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Aug 2021 10:13:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Dec 2022 17:06:14 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 9 May 2023 08:24:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-10"}
