ing for cluster-cluster growth. The\n(TiO$_2$)$_N$ cluster growth efficiency has a sweet-spot temperature at\n$\\approx 1000$K at which CCN formation is triggered. The combination of local\nthermodynamic conditions and chemical processes therefore determines CCN\nformation efficiency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Aug 2021 14:01:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-27"}
